\c 23
\nb
\v 1 UBalami wasesithi kuBalaki: Ngakhela lapha amalathi ayisikhombisa, ungilungisele lapha amajongosi ayisikhombisa lenqama eziyisikhombisa\x + 23.29. 1 Lan. 15.26. Jobe 42.8.\x*.
\v 2 UBalaki wenza njengokutsho kukaBalami; uBalaki loBalami basebenikela ku\add lelo lalelo\add* ilathi ijongosi lenqama\x + 23.4,14,30.\x*.
\v 3 UBalami wasesithi kuBalaki: Mana emnikelweni wakho wokutshiswa\x + 23.15.\x*, ngizahamba mina; mhlawumbe iN\nd kosi\nd* izafika ukungihlangabeza; lento ezangitshengisa yona ngizakutshela\x + 24.1.\x*. Wasesiya endaweni ephakemeyo.
\v 4 UNkulunkulu wasehlangana loBalami\x + 23.16.\x*; wasesithi kuye: Sengilungise amalathi ayisikhombisa, nganikela ku\add lelo lalelo\add* ilathi ijongosi lenqama.
\v 5 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasifaka ilizwi emlonyeni kaBalami, yathi: Buyela kuBalaki, ukhulume kanje\x + 22.38; 23.12,16. Isa. 51.16; 59.21. Dute. 18.18. Jer. 1.9.\x*.
\v 6 Wasebuyela kuye, khangela-ke, wayemi emnikelweni wakhe wokutshiswa, yena lazo zonke iziphathamandla zakoMowabi.
\v 7 Wasephakamisa umzekeliso wakhe, wathi:
\p UBalaki, inkosi yakoMowabi, ungilandile eSiriya\f + \fk eSiriya: \fl Heb. \fqa eAramu\f*, ezintabeni zempumalanga \add wathi\x + 23.18; 24.3,15,20,23; 21.27.\x*\add*: Woza, ungiqalekisele uJakobe\x + 22.6.\x*, woza, umthuke uIsrayeli\x + Isa. 66.14. Mal. 1.4.\x*.
\v 8 Ngingamqalekisa njani\x + 22.11,17.\x* uNkulunkulu anga\add m\add*qalekisiyo?\x + 22.11,17.\x* Kumbe ngingamthuka njani iN\nd kosi\nd* enga\add m\add*thukanga?
\v 9 Ngoba ngisengqongeni yamadwala ngiyambona, ngisemaqaqeni ngiyamkhangela. Khangela, abantu bazahlala bodwa\x + Dute. 33.28.\x*, kabayikubalelwa phakathi kwezizwe\x + Eks. 33.16. Ezra 9.2. Efe. 2.14.\x*.
\v 10 Ngubani ongabala uthuli lukaJakobe\x + Gen. 13.16.\x*, lenani lengxenye yesine kaIsrayeli? Umphefumulo wami kawufe ukufa kwabalungileyo\x + Hlab. 116.15.\x*, lokuphela kwami kube njengokwakhe!
\p
\v 11 UBalaki wasesithi kuBalami: Wenzeni kimi? Ngikuthethe ukuze uqalekise izitha zami, kodwa khangela, u\add zi\add*busisile loku\add zi\add*busisa\x + 22.11,17; 24.10. Dute. 23.5.\x*.
\v 12 Wasephendula wathi: Lokho iN\nd kosi\nd* ekufaka emlonyeni wami, kakumelanga ngiqaphele yini ukukukhuluma?\x + 22.38. 23.5.\x*
\v 13 UBalaki wasesithi kuye: Ake uze lami siye kwenye indawo lapho ozababona khona; uzabona ukucina kwabo kuphela, ungaboni bonke; njalo ungiqalekisele bona ulapho.
\p
\v 14 Njalo wamthatha wamusa ensimini yeZofimu, engqongeni yePisiga; wakha amalathi ayisikhombisa, wanikela ijongosi lenqama phezu kwa\add lelo lalelo\add* ilathi\x + 23.1,2.\x*.
\v 15 Wasesithi kuBalaki: Mana lapha emnikelweni wakho wokutshiswa, njalo mina ngizahlangana \add layo\add* laphayana\x + 23.3,4,16.\x*.
\v 16 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasihlangana loBalami, yafaka ilizwi emlonyeni wakhe\x + 22.35. 23.5.\x*, yathi: Buyela kuBalaki, ukhulume kanje.
\v 17 Esefikile kuye, khangela-ke wema emnikelweni wakhe wokutshiswa leziphathamandla zakoMowabi zilaye. UBalaki wasesithi kuye: IN\nd kosi\nd* itheni?
\v 18 Wasephakamisa umfanekiso wakhe wathi:
\p Sukuma, Balaki, uzwe, ubeke indlebe, ndodana kaZipori.
\v 19 UNkulunkulu kasumuntu ukuthi aqambe amanga\x + 1 Sam. 15.29. Mal. 3.6. Roma 11.29. Tit. 1.2. Jak. 1.17.\x*, loba indodana yomuntu ukuthi azisole. Utshilo, kanti kayikukwenza? Kumbe ukhulumile, kanti kayikukuqinisa?
\v 20 Khangela, ngemukele ukuthi ngibusise; yebo, ubusisile, njalo ngingeke ngikuguqule\x + 22.12. Gen. 12.3; 22.17.\x*.
\v 21 Kakhangelanga ububi kuJakobe, kabonanga isiphambeko kuIsrayeli\x + Jobe 4.8; 15.35. Hlab. 7.14; 10.7,14,.\x*. IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe ilaye, lesimemezelo senkosi siphakathi kwakhe\x + Hlab. 89.15.\x*.
\v 22 UNkulunkulu wabakhupha eGibhithe\x + 24.8.\x*, ulokunjengamandla\x + Jobe 22.25. Hlab. 95.4.\x* enyathi\x + Dute. 33.17. Hlab. 29.6; 92.10. Isa. 34.7. Jobe 39.10,11. Hlab. 22.21.\x*.
\v 23 Isibili kakulamlingo ongamelana loJakobe, loba ukuvumisa okungamelana loIsrayeli\x + Dute. 18.10. 22.7.\x*. Ngalesisikhathi kuzatshiwo ngoJakobe langoIsrayeli ukuthi uNkulunkulu akwenzileyo\x + Hlab. 44.1.\x*!
\v 24 Khangela, abantu bazasukuma njengesilwane esisikazi\x + Gen. 49.9.\x*, bazisukumise njengesilwane\x + Gen. 49.9.\x*; kabalali baze badle impango, njalo banathe igazi lababuleweyo\x + Gen. 49.27.\x*.
\p
\v 25 UBalaki wasesithi kuBalami: Futhi ungabaqalekisi lokubaqalekisa, njalo ungababusisi lokubabusisa.
\v 26 Kodwa uBalami waphendula wathi kuBalaki: Kangikutshelanga yini ngisithi: Konke iN\nd kosi\nd* ekutshoyo, lokho ngizakwenza?\x + 22.18.\x*
\p
\v 27 UBalaki wasesithi kuBalami: Ake uze, ngizakusa kwenye indawo\x + 23.13.\x*; mhlawumbe kungaqonda emehlweni kaNkulunkulu ukuthi ungiqalekisele bona ulapho.
\v 28 UBalaki wamthatha wamusa uBalami engqongeni yePeyori\x + 25.18; 31.16. Josh. 22.17. 25.3,5. Dute. 4.3. Hlab. 106.28. Hos. 9.10.\x* ekhangele ngasenkangala\x + 21.20.\x*.
\v 29 UBalami wasesithi kuBalaki: Ngakhela lapha amalathi ayisikhombisa, ungilungisele lapha amajongosi ayisikhombisa lenqama eziyisikhombisa\x + 23.1,2.\x*.
\v 30 UBalaki wasesenza njengokutsho kukaBalami, wanikela ijongosi lenqama ku\add lelo lalelo\add* ilathi\x + 23.1,2.\x*.
